about: Hi! I'm a Computer Science student at Georgia Tech with a passion for software development, machine learning, and problem-solving. Proficient in Python and Java, I have applied my skills to machine learning models and full-stack applications. I thrive in collaborative environments, leading technical projects and optimizing solutions through data-driven insights. Outside of academics, I enjoy exploring new technologies and working on side projects to enhance my skills. My goal is to contribute to innovative software solutions that improve efficiency and user experience.
